HEADWORD: Representativeness
<hw>Rep`re*sent"a*tive*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or
state of being representative.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Dr. Burnet observes, that every thought is attended with
consciousness and <qex>representativeness</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Spectator.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

